name: Amatsu-Mikaboshi
description: Many years ago, a great god was born. Through the experiences we have gathered, we keep coming back. We are stronger and more hungry now than ever before. I can see the doubt in your hearts, let me prove my superiority. I may not be him, but I am a relative of the one you call king. Amatsu- Mikaboshi was reborn. There are hundreds of scammers out there today, but we are the ancestors. We are the birthplace of the beautiful land that survives today.
